com.skratchdot.electribe.model.esx

Interface GlobalParameters

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GlobalParametersImpl

    public interface GlobalParameters
    A representation of the model object 'Global Parameters'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Memory Protect Enabled
    • Reserved Byte
    • Arpeggiator Control
    • Audio In Mode
    • Midi Clock
    • Note Message Enabled
    • System Ex Enabled
    • Control Change Enabled
    • Program Change Enabled
    • Reserved Bits After Program Change Enabled
    • Pitch Bend Range
    • Midi Channels
    • Part Note Numbers
    • Midi Control Change Assignments
    • Reserved Long
    • Pattern Set Parameters

    See Also:
    EsxPackage.getGlobalParameters()
